P_HTM[668]="*pāpikā icchā na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ pāpikā icchā abhibhuyya iriyatī’ti.**or corrupt wishes, so corrupt wishes master them and keep going.’*";
P_HTM[669]="*Tañce, bhikkhave, bhikkhuṃ lobho nābhibhuyya iriyati,**Suppose that greed does not master that mendicant and keep going.*";
