P_HTM[680]="*‘tathā ayamāyasmā pajānāti yathā pajānato lobho na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ lobho nābhibhuyya iriyati;**‘This venerable has the understanding that eliminates greed, so greed doesn’t master them and keep going.*";
P_HTM[681]="*tathā ayamāyasmā pajānāti yathā pajānato doso na hoti …**They have the understanding that eliminates hate …*";
