P_HTM[709]="*‘nāyamāyasmā tathā pajānāti yathā pajānato lobho na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ lobho abhibhuyya tiṭṭhati;**‘This venerable does not have the understanding that would eliminate greed, so greed masters them and keeps going.*";
