P_HTM[718]="*pāpikā icchā na hoti, tathāhimaṃ āyasmantaṃ pāpikā icchā abhibhuyya tiṭṭhatī’ti.**or corrupt wishes, so corrupt wishes master them and keep going.’*";
P_HTM[719]="*Bhāvanāvādaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu vadamāno:**A mendicant who makes a declaration of development says:*";
P_HTM[720]="*‘bhāvitakāyomhi bhāvitasīlo bhāvitacitto bhāvitapañño’ti.**‘I am developed in physical endurance, ethics, mind, and wisdom.’*";
