P_HTM[6168]="*Rāgapeyyālaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ.* **";
P_HTM[6169]="*Pañcamo paṇṇāsako samatto.* **";
P_HTM[6170]="*Dasakanipātapāḷi niṭṭhitā.**The Book of the Tens is finished.*";
